// Each item contains:
//   item_id          — UUID unique identifier
//   stem             — The question text shown to the learner
//   options          — Array of 4 answer choices (indices 0–3)
//   correct_choice   — Index of the correct option (0–3)
//   skill            — Top-level category: Grammar | Vocabulary | Reading
//   sub_skill        — Granular tag (e.g. "Verb Tenses", "Collocations")
//   cefr_difficulty   — CEFR level: A2 | B1 | B2 | C1
