//   irt_b_param      — IRT difficulty parameter (the ability level where P(correct) = 0.5)
//   irt_c_param      — IRT guessing parameter (probability of getting it right by chance)
//   explanation_text — Plain-English explanation shown in wrong-answer review
//   distractor_traps — Maps each wrong option index to why learners pick it
//   goal_tags        — Which goal types (A–E) this item is especially diagnostic for
//
// V1 (items 1–100):   A2=16, B1=34, B2=28, C1=22 | Grammar=40, Vocabulary=35, Reading=25
